description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-The Kirkjufell mountain and waterfalls
-Godafoss in  the Northern lights
-The historic town of Husavik
-Ice Cave in Vatnajokull
-Seljalandsfoss
-Blooming lupine flowers on the Stokksnes
-Lava of Fagradalsfjall
-Hvitserkur troll rock
-Studlagil Canyon
-Icebergs in Jokulsarlon
name: Iceland - Most beautiful places in the World -
